  "synopsis": "Wu Chen is stuck in an endless time loop, reliving the same day over and over again—July 7th, 2020. No matter what he does, the clock resets. Over a thousand years, he's mastered hundreds of languages and every instrument imaginable, and perfected skills in fighting, driving, shooting, cooking, dancing, acting...and more. But on this very day, something changes. July 8th, 2020 finally arrives...\n\n(Source: WebComics)",
